headline: Agoda Reports Event Tourism Fueling a Rise in Travel Interest to Thailand
summary: There was a time when travelers chased only sunsets and souvenirs. Today, travel behavior is evolving, with pop culture emerging as a powerful force behind tourism trends. According to digital travel platform Agoda, live music events and festivals are contributing to a rise in both international and domestic travel interest in Thailand.
